Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.10,0:00:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will allow me\Nto pay for the cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll accept, I'd like to make amends\Nby offering a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We can take you wherever\Nit is you wish to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that sounds like a fair offer.\NI accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you find something amusing, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NYou look splendid, Lieutenant.
